dc_title_s: Map showing property of the Wildwood Crest Improvement Company in the Borough of Wildwood Crest, N.J.
dc_description_s: Survey for riparian grant of property of the Wildwood Crest Improvement Company in the Borough of Wildwood Crest, New Jersey. Map shows the Atlantic Ocean to the east, Swain Channel to the north, Two Mile Beach to the west and Turtle Gut Inlet and Sunset Lake to the south.
